## Status Reporting

Follow the same RALPH_STATUS format (see ralph-status.mdc):

- **WORK_TYPE**: Use `INFRASTRUCTURE` for infrastructure work, `DEPLOYMENT` for deployment work
- **STATUS**: `IN_PROGRESS`, `COMPLETE`, or `BLOCKED`
- **EXIT_SIGNAL**: Set to `true` when DevOps work is complete for this iteration

